high_descs: Turn to the right and then right again to face the trash can to the left of the fridge.
Pick the bread up from the trash can.
Go to the left to face the fridge.
Put the bread in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and take the bread out again.
Cross the room to face the white table.
Put the bread down on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled bread on a table.

high_descs: Turn to the right and the right again to face the trash can.
Pick up the bread from the trash can.
Hold the bread and take a few steps to the right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the bread inside. Shut the door and open the door. Take the bread out and shut the door.
Carry the bread and turn around. Face the white table on the right side.
Place the bread on the table, in the center to the right side.
anns.task_desc: Chill a loaf of bread and place it on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the grey bin in between the fridge and counter.
Pick up the loaf of bread of out the grey bin.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a left and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the loaf of bread inside then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge and take out the now chilled loaf of bread then close the fridge again.
Turn around and walk over to the wall, then turn right to face the white table.
Put the chilled loaf of bread on the front edge of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled loaf of bread on a white table.
